00:00:12.070 --> 00:00:14.890
The new developer
tools security panel

00:00:14.890 --> 00:00:18.230
makes it easier to debug
mixed content issues

00:00:18.230 --> 00:00:22.850
and ensure your site is
properly served over HTTPS.

00:00:22.850 --> 00:00:27.010
And you can now add presentation
mode to mobile apps,

00:00:27.010 --> 00:00:30.850
easily casting content
